schemeParserFactories

public JsonObject schemeParserFactories()
Get the JsonObject where SchemeParserFactories are stored. This is a method used during bootstrapping to get hold of the scheme parsers - since the scheme parsers are required in order to decode a URL and find a value, we have to give a direct reference that the system can itself store in a location during bootstrapping.

Returns:
The JsonObject where SchemeParserFactories are stored.
